## 📋 Project Requirements Checklist
- [x] **Fully functioning backend:** Built with FastAPI (Python).
- [x] **Real-world use case:** Smart food management and waste reduction.
- [x] **API Layer:** RESTful API with endpoints for inventory and recipes.
- [x] **Application Logic:** Logic to filter expired vs. fresh items and match ingredients.
- [x] **Database:** SQLite with SQLAlchemy ORM for persistent storage.
- [x] **External API:** Integrated with the **Spoonacular API** for real-time recipe data.
- [x] **Cloud Deployment:** Backend hosted on **Render**, Frontend on **Streamlit Cloud**.
- [x] **Connected Client:** Interactive web interface built with **Streamlit**.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Backend:** FastAPI (Python)
- **Database:** SQLite (SQLAlchemy)
- **Frontend:** Streamlit
- **External Integration:** Spoonacular API
- **Deployment:** Render (Backend) & Streamlit Cloud (Frontend)

